remarks:
Multiplication of complex numbers is associative.  Axiom 10 of 22 for real and complex numbers, derived from ZF set theory.  This construction-dependent theorem should not be referenced directly; instead, use ~ ax-mulass .  (Contributed by NM, 3-Sep-1995.) (New usage is discouraged.)

 Multiplication of complex numbers is associative.  Axiom for real and complex numbers, derived from set theory.  This construction-dependent theorem should not be referenced directly; instead, use ~ ax-mulass . (Contributed by NM, 3-Sep-1995.)  (New usage is discouraged.)
statement: axmulass $p |- ( ( A e. CC /\ B e. CC /\ C e. CC ) -> ( ( A x. B ) x. C ) = ( A x. ( B x. C ) ) ) $.
